77:// IsAlreadyLoggedIn returns true if err indicates the character is already connected.
78://
79:// Precondition: err may be nil or non-nil.
80:// Postcondition: Returns true only when the error message contains "already connected".
81:func IsAlreadyLoggedIn(err error) bool {
82:	return err != nil && strings.Contains(err.Error(), "already connected")
83:}
