85:// IsRandomInput reports whether the player's input at a list step requests random selection.
86:// Blank input, "r", and "random" (all case-insensitive) are treated as random.
87:// Exported for testing.
88:func IsRandomInput(s string) bool {
89:	lower := strings.ToLower(strings.TrimSpace(s))
90:	return lower == "" || lower == "r" || lower == "random"
91:}
